================================================================================
THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES
================================================================================

Poindexter depends on a number of open-source libraries. The full dependency
manifests live in:

  - src/cofounder_agent/pyproject.toml  (Python backend)
  - package.json                        (Node tooling)
  - mcp-server/pyproject.toml           (MCP server)

Notable dependencies and their licenses:

  - FastAPI                MIT License
  - asyncpg                Apache License 2.0
  - PostgreSQL + pgvector  PostgreSQL License (permissive)
  - Pydantic               MIT License
  - httpx                  BSD-3-Clause
  - Ollama                 MIT License
  - CrewAI                 MIT License
  - Grafana OSS            AGPL 3.0
  - Prometheus             Apache License 2.0
  - Next.js                MIT License (frontend, not shipped in public repo)

This list is not exhaustive — it covers the most architecturally significant
dependencies. See each component's own repository or distribution for the
complete and authoritative license terms.

